reviewText: Somebody stole this from my house. I need this back but I need it in DVD form instead of VHS.
These videos are what is out there people! Want to know how the rest of the world is.... watch some of this! We live waaaaaaaaay better!

This documentary shows the reality of life at its worst. This film is not recommended for those who have a weak stomach.  If you love hanging on the edge of your seat this is the film for you!  This film has it all from people up in flames, death defining falls, life and death shootings, out of control animals, and some sex crazed women.  This is a MUST SEE flick about the Facts of Life.
